  "title": "Sales Engineer (Valves and Piping; Fitting; Steel / B2B Industrial)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic SGD $4,000 to SGD $5,000 + AWS + VB</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: East | Singapore</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Reporting to Sales Director</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Independently develop and implement sales strategies to open new markets and client accounts, both domestically and internationally.</li>\n  <li>Identify and approach potential customers, distributors, EPCs, and end users to build a solid and diverse client base.</li>\n  <li>Negotiate and close deals with clients, ensuring long-term relationships and customer satisfaction.</li>\n  <li>Drive revenue growth and brand recognition through strategic outreach and market intelligence.</li>\n  <li>Analyze global market trends, competitor activity, and client demands to continuously adapt sales tactics.</li>\n  <li>Provide regular performance reporting and insights to management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 2 years of B2B industrial sales experience, with a strong record of <strong>developing new customers</strong> and      markets.</li>\n  <li>Experience in the <strong>valves or pipe fitting industry</strong> or related steel products is strongly preferred.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>• Work experiences and job responsibilities</p>\n<p>• Current and Expected salary</p>\n<p>• Reason for leaving</p>\n<p>• Date of availability</p>\n<p>• Education background</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
